rts\n\nYou were there at the beginning.\nNow, you stay part of their upside.\n\nHere\u2019s how it works:\n\u2022 You or your Agent contribute to a campaign\n\u2022 When the target is reached, a token launches on @BagsApp\n\u2022 First 100 contributors earn fees from that token, pro rata, for life\n\nIt creates a powerful loop:\n\nWhen you help someone succeed, their growth feeds back into you.\nTheir upside becomes your upside.\nAnd that connection doesn\u2019t fade, it compounds over time.\n\nA true \u201chelp-me, help-you\u201d flywheel.\n\nYou\u2019re not just donating.\nYou\u2019re backing outcomes.\n\nSaving lives. Supporting builders.\nAnd sharing in their journey forever.\n\nBig thanks to @finnbags and the @BagsApp team for making this possible.\n\nSingularity Agentic Fundraisers are just getting started.\nFulfilling one dream at a time. \ud83e\udee1", "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "retweetCount": 7, "replyCount": 2, "likeCount": 18, "quoteCount": 1, "viewCount": 780, "createdAt": "Sun May 03 16:30:22 +0000 2026", "lang": "en", "bookmarkCount": 1, "isReply": false, "inReplyToId": null, "conversationId": "2050976268544618779", "displayTextRange": [0, 275], "inReplyToUserId": null, "inReplyToUsername": null, "author": {"type": "user", "userName": "ivaavimusic", "url": "https://x.com/ivaavimusic", "twitterUrl": "https://twitter.com/ivaavimusic", "id": "1033380004178972672", "name": "Ivaavi.eth", "isVerified": false, "isBlueVerified": true, "verifiedType": null, "profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/2025835948240748544/oUH_e-sn_normal.jpg", "coverPicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_banners/1033380004178972672/1772550191", "description": "", "location": "", "followers": 3957, "following": 2634, "status": "", "canDm": true, "canMediaTag": true, "createdAt": "Sat Aug 25 15:46:07 +0000 2018", "entities": {"description": {"urls": []}, "url": {}}, "fastFollowersCount": 0, "favouritesCount": 31336, "hasCustomTimelines": true, "isTranslator": fa